---
title: Creamy Chickpea & Cauliflower Stew with Roasted Kumara & Couscous
description: When we first tried this bright burst of goodness, we all agreed it had that "hug in a bowl" kind of feeling. There's wholesome chickpeas, kumara and spinach, plus a sublime, lightly spiced creamy sauce that soaks into the couscous. Enjoy!
